<p><strong>Speed</strong> 30 ft.<br/><strong>Melee</strong> mwk rapier +10/+5 (1d6-1/18-20) or mwk rapier +8/+3 (1d6-1/18-20), mwk dagger +8 (1d4-1/19-20)<br/><strong>Ranged</strong> mwk dagger +10 (1d4-1/19-20)</p>
